typedef struct QSPI_memConfig_t QSPI_memConfig

QSPI memory map configuration.

The structure has all the fields needed to configure QSPI in memory mapped mode

typedef struct QSPI_Params_t QSPI_Params

QSPI Parameters.

QSPI Parameters are used to with the QSPI_open() call. Default values for these parameters are set using QSPI_Params_init().

See also
QSPI_Params_init()
